NAME

    App::CPANCoverBadge - Get badge for cpancover

VERSION

    version 0.03

SYNOPSIS

        use App::CPANCoverBadge;
    
        my $badger = App::CPANCoverBadge->new;
        my $badge  = $badger->badge( 'App-CPANCoverBadge-0.01' );
        
        say $badge;

ATTRIBUTES

      * db_file

      * sql

      * ua

METHODS

 badge

AUTHOR

    Renee Baecker <reneeb@cpan.org>

